Despite the decline in investment, Sun Yi believes that Chinese companies are still very interested in Germany. In the report, she pointed out: "Most of the transactions that have occurred in recent years are very successful. In this context, China and Germany have now established a close and flexible connection on many levels." She believes that there will be more Chinese companies this year Looking for acquisition objects in Europe. "However, the number of transactions will still be significantly lower than the period of prosperity."

