The statement said that "the best way to protect Tibetans from being exempted from Chinese autocratic rule is to promote peacefully to solve illegal occupation of Tibet by Tibet." The statement also suggested that the United States can promote the resolution of the Tibet-China Conflict Act in the two parties of the Congress.

