### qigong fever and "Falun Gong"

In the 1990s, China set off a national qigong, and the "Falun Gong" from Jilin Province was quickly spread during this period, becoming one of the most influential cultivation groups. The picture shows a Falun Gong practitioner in a square in Guangzhou.

