### Large -scale arrest operation

Starting on July 20, 1999, the actions of arresting Falun Gong practitioners were launched in China. On July 22, Beijing officially released the "Decision of the Ministry of Civil Affairs of the People's Republic of China on the Falun Dafa Research Association". While official media began to criticize Falun Gong, a large number of Falun Gong practitioners were arrested. Western countries such as the United States have called on the Chinese government to adopt "restraint attitude".

