After Falun Gong was announced to ban, with the deepening of arrest and suppression, there are also sporadic protests from Falun Gong practitioners from all over China. The picture shows a Falun Gong protesters arrested by a plainclothes police at Tiananmen Square on October 1, 2000.

*![](Images/dwzh/2023-05-27T10-26-00Z/49646942_303.jpg)#
